data.description:
$10,000+ in upgrades & restorations have been invested in 2024! This provides you with an exceptional opportunity to immerse yourself in the tranquil ambiance of a forest-like setting, situated on 20+ acres in the heart of Mandarin. Yet within close proximity to amenities such as restaurants, shopping, the YMCA & many other recreational options. The upper floor hosts the owner's suite along with 2 additional bedrooms & a full bathroom. The expansive patio serves as the perfect retreat for relaxation or spending time with friends & family. The TOWNHOMES of Bigtree community provides amenities such as a pool, spa, pavilion & a picnic area for your ultimate enjoyment. Additionally, there is a dedicated space for your boat, trailer or other cherished recreational items. Discover the serenity of the lake/retention pond, where you can pause and appreciate the presence of fish, birds & turtles. Enjoy the process of transforming this space into a home that you love! High end vinyl floors -2021
New carpeting upstairs-4/2023
New kitchen sink faucet and garbage disposal
Newer oven range
New fan in living room
New garbage can pull out under sink
New light fixture in second bedroom
Inside Electric panel-2018
GFCI receptacles: kitchen, bathroom downstairs and owner's bathroom
Owner's bathroom has new shower head, toilet seat and faucet
New shut off valves in all bathrooms
 Air conditioning blower motor replaced 10/2020
Two new windows in 1st guest bedroom 2023
Refrigerator- 2019 (AS IS)
Washer & dryer -2021 (AS IS)

      2024: almost $10,000 in RESTORATIONS:
Exterior Main Disconnect Replaced 
Air Conditioner Condenser moved 2  feet from electrical box, 
new copper, new foam, 1 lb freon added
Conduit for garbage disposal replaced 
pipe under sink replaced 
Threshold padding added
Outside faucet replaced
Replaced old smoke alarm  
Firewall patched
Replaced soffit
Door frame at front door replaced 
New windows: 3 in 2nd bedroom and 1 in Owner's Suite 
Roof repaired
